~ start
Vagabond: I suppose we should have told you sooner. Normally, we would have directed you towards the village in the west where most of us have taken up residence.
Vagabond: In fact, it's a short walk east of here. Had you arrived under better circumstances, the commune would be more than willing to assist you in getting settled.
Vagabond: Once the False Heroes began their reign of terror though, many of us were forced out of the village as they wanted to use it as a base of operations.
Vagabond: We know not what has become of it. Some of us were unable to escape in time, and The Fighter and Mage have been preventing us from entering.
Vagabond: However, there are three of us now. Not to mention one of us who has already slain one of the fiends. This is the best opportunity we've had yet.
set TalkScenes.zulie_talk.dialogue_resource = load("res://dialogue/zulie_cut5_4.dialogue")
do TalkScenes.zulie_talk.start()
=> END